{"id":"79265c3c-b26c-4751-8bf5-0f63a73772ab","name":"Excommunicated","description":"<p>You've uncovered a slave trafficking ring involving a high-ranking clergyman...</p><p>Your reward? Banishment...</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(158, 158, 158);\"><strong>\"I'm sorry... I can't believe you... He would never do that\"</strong></span></p><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PidLodM2AhZf6j9PbpcLV.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>✦</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(139, 139, 139);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 170, 77);\"><strong>───</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(139, 139, 139);\"><strong> SUMMARY </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 170, 77);\"><strong>───</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(139, 139, 139);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>✦</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\"><strong>After investigating disappearances within the Sacrum Ordo Aeterni, you uncover a secret slave-trafficking scheme connected to High Cleric Elstein. Upon rescuing Fedora from the Church’s hidden dungeons and sheltering her in your own home for her safety and because of suspicions about how far the corruption within the very forces you are fighting might reach hiding her becomes your best option.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\"><strong>You file a formal accusation against Elstein, but the trial turns against you.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\"><strong>Politically manipulated, publicly discredited, and betrayed by the silence of your allies, you are excommunicated.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\"><strong